Package: meerai
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.10), python3-venv
Description: MeerAI - Your AI that watches while you rest
 MeerAI is an AI-powered system agent that monitors your infrastructure
 and handles routine tasks autonomously, so you can sleep through the night.
 .
 Features:
  - Proactive system monitoring with configurable triggers
  - Policy-controlled autonomy levels (observe, suggest, confirm, auto)
  - Natural language interface for system administration
  - Audit logging of all actions
  - Integration with existing tools (Prometheus, systemd, etc.)
